data.description: This is your chance to own a beautiful 1920's style Bungalow that offers the historic charm of built-in's and hardwoods without sacrificing the modern amenities, home even has air conditioning. Charming home with beautiful woodwork throughout. High ceilings for a more spacious feel. 3 bedrooms on one level. Plus a main level office/den with french doors. Formal dining and a large living room make it great for entertaining. Enjoy your privacy at your bonfire pit with paved patio in your fenced large yard! OFFER DEADLINE MONDAY, APRIL 15 AT 6 PM
